{"word":"ἀφυλακτέω","slug":"ἀφυλακτέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀφυλακτέω1</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <el>ἀφ-ὑλακτέω</el>\n<p/><i>to bark out</i> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>luc.</a></b><p/> <hr/> <el><b>ἀφυλακτέω2</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <a href='S:ἀφύλακτος'><el>ἀφύλακτος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to be off one's guard</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to be careless about</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}